reviews.review_text: Nice smooth jam! What a show! Nice smooth tight jams, Keith's keyboard playing is on the ball, Jerry’s smooth style playing is tame and clean here and I really like it, Donna holds back at just the right times as well. It’s the kind of show that just makes you feel good; space out and lay back on the grass. The pitch is a tad high but this is really a great jam.
